        Selling a Deceased Estate in Brisbane: What Executors Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Selling a property as part of a deceased estate involves probate, executor authority, and careful coordination across legal, family, and real estate processes. Here is what to expect.
